Business problem understanding

  • -A car dealership chain wants to increase its monthly sales and improve profitability. Management wants to understand:

-Which car models sell the most and least?

-How price, engine size, mileage, and brand affect sales.

-What discounts or marketing strategy will increase sales?

df.loc[df['manufacturer']=='Acura','power_perf_factor']=(
    df.loc[df['manufacturer']=='Acura','power_perf_factor'].fillna(Acura__m))

  • Cars with higher performance factors slightly maintain better resale values.
